metadata.name: Non-Fungible Ticket #1
metadata.description: Access to the Non-Fungible Conference on April 4th & 5th, 2022 from 9am-6pm on both days. ArtWork by @neurocolor and @XCOPYART Thanks to @CultCryptoArt lead by @EclecticMethod who are co-editing the conference with help from @XCOPYART & @neurocolor. NFT Ticket must be in the Metamask mobile wallet for entry/redemption.
